INVOICER

This is a local-first invoice management platform.

If you only want to use the app, open the GitHub repository releases page and download Invoicer.html from the latest release. Then double-click Invoicer.html to open it in your browser.

GitHub repository:
https://github.com/Alienoghli/invoicer

For setup instructions, features, usage guide, privacy notes, and developer information, read README.md.

This project works best in desktop view.
